data.description: Experience elevated living in this impressive Like-New two-story home situated on a sprawling 1-acre lot. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, this residence exudes modern elegance and thoughtful design. The exterior showcases durable and stylish Vinyl Siding, along with architectural roof shingles, ensuring both durability and an aesthetic appeal. Step into a luminous foyer featuring SPC plank flooring, setting the tone for the open-concept floor plan that seamlessly connects the family room, dining area, and kitchen. The kitchen is a chef's dream, adorned with granite countertops and equipped with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Ascend the oak steps with no carpet on the stairs, complemented by wrought iron balusters, adding a touch of sophistication to the interior. This property combines stylish features, quality craftsmanship, and a spacious layout to create a welcoming and luxurious home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this dream property yours!
